OOC: Forgive my absence. I was on an abrupt vacation with my family. I read 
394 e mails today and it was alot of information to absorb in a short matter 
of time so do excuse me if I seem confused and out of it. Thank you.

::: Hell Beast glances around the bridge. Scince Set and Ra retreated, they 
returned into the ship. Marine, Black Aracnia, and Pheniox were being treated 
to a dip in the CR tanks while everyone else ran the operations of the ship. 
:::

::: Transanulas, at the main computer system ::: Hell Beast, everything looks 
clear. For the moment at least.

::: Jackle and Gremlin sat at the computers on the right and left side of the 
bridge. ::: Commander, he's right. Scans are clear for the moment.

::: Hell Beast nodded. The past few day have been quite hazy. :::

::: Hell Beast ::: Alright. Megatron, Zardus, and myself never had our 
negotiations yet. Get Megatron here now.

::: After a few minutes, Megatron entered :::

::: Megatron ::: Can I be of some service?

::: Hell Beast ::: Were going to meet with Zardus. I think he said in the 
jungle, by some out cropping. ...well, he can meet us there. Send the 
transmission.

::: Gremlin nods and sends the message to meet Hell Beast and Megatron in the 
jungle by the giant outcropping rock. :::
